snippet.textDisplay:
It baffles me to the core that someone with the talent and skills of Naseebo Lal would resort to singing B-grade songs for so long. She is a powerhouse, an intensity 6 storm.
About this song. Gosh! Mind blowing is such an understatement. The genius of Xulfi. The production. Next level stuff. But above all that is the magic of Naseebo Lal and Abida Parveen. Naseebo Lal has done something that cannot be described in words. It was the giant Abida Parveen who stood her ground in front of her. Had it been anybody else, Naseebo had blown her away in seconds. Wow! Pure genius. Whoa!
